_header: Of death and life which be in strife to treat I now intend

OxfMagd213.First Lines:
Off deathe and lyfffe whiche Be in stryfe to treate now I
                    intendeBothe man and wyffe corne grasse and chyse beginning taketh
                    ende…
OxfMagd213.Last Lines:
…Lusty coraige doo not oute Raige though god haue sent the
                    myghtWythe euery Aige both w[ ] and saige Dethe is Redy to
                    ffygh
